"OKAY, THAT'S JUST A BAD DREAM."

35:43.900 --> 35:46.567
**

35:46.567 --> 35:49.300
I HAD FOUND OUT THAT

35:46.567 --> 35:49.300
ACTUALLY SEEING

35:49.300 --> 35:51.900
SOME SORT OF BLACK DOG

35:49.300 --> 35:51.900
IN THE PRISON

35:51.900 --> 35:55.300
IS AN ENCOUNTER

35:51.900 --> 35:55.300
THAT PEOPLE HAVE HAD.

35:55.300 --> 35:58.700
THEY ARE SEEN IN GRAVEYARDS,

35:55.300 --> 35:58.700
CEMETERIES,

35:58.700 --> 36:00.833
PLACES OF EXECUTION --

36:00.833 --> 36:02.200
WHEREVER THERE'S BEEN

36:00.833 --> 36:02.200
A LOT OF DEATH,

36:02.200 --> 36:05.067
THAT'S WHERE THEY'RE SEEN.

36:05.067 --> 36:08.900
I HAD NO CLUE THAT ANYBODY HAD

36:05.067 --> 36:08.900
EVER HAD ANY SORT OF EXPERIENCE

36:08.900 --> 36:12.533
WITH WHAT WOULD BE KNOWN

36:08.900 --> 36:12.533
AS A HELLHOUND IN THE PRISON.

36:12.533 --> 36:15.133
**

36:15.133 --> 36:20.200
SO, FOR ME, THAT KIND OF ADDED

36:15.133 --> 36:20.200
A LITTLE BIT OF VALIDATION

36:20.200 --> 36:22.533
TO WHAT I HAD EXPERIENCED

36:22.533 --> 36:25.833
TO KNOW THAT OTHER PEOPLE

36:22.533 --> 36:25.833
HAD SEEN THE SAME THING I DID,

36:25.833 --> 36:27.467
ALTHOUGH

36:25.833 --> 36:27.467
I DIDN'T SEE IT THERE --

36:27.467 --> 36:29.967
I SAW IT IN MY HOME.

36:29.967 --> 36:34.533
**

