36:51.100 --> 36:55.233
I LET MY DOG OUT

36:51.100 --> 36:55.233
EARLY IN THE MORNING...

36:55.233 --> 36:58.067
JAKE!

36:58.067 --> 37:00.500
FOOD'S READY, BOY!

37:00.500 --> 37:05.733
**

37:05.733 --> 37:08.567
JAKE!

37:08.567 --> 37:11.233
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

37:11.233 --> 37:12.367
BOBBY!

37:12.367 --> 37:15.367
[ Voice breaking ]

37:12.367 --> 37:15.367
...AND WOULD NOT GET UP.

37:15.367 --> 37:16.800
BOBBY!

37:16.800 --> 37:18.533
**

