38:24.067 --> 38:31.067
**

38:31.067 --> 38:32.933
[ BREATHES SHARPLY ]

38:32.933 --> 38:37.067
[ Crying ] SO, WE GOT TO

38:32.933 --> 38:37.067
THE VET'S OFFICE EARLY SATURDAY.

38:37.067 --> 38:44.100
**

38:44.100 --> 38:47.267
THEY GIVE HIM SOME MEDICATION,

38:44.100 --> 38:47.267
SOME STEROIDS,

38:47.267 --> 38:48.600
TO TRY TO SEE

38:48.600 --> 38:54.533
IF IT WOULD HELP HIM GET

38:48.600 --> 38:54.533
SOME FEELING BACK INTO HIS LEGS,

38:54.533 --> 38:56.200
AND IT DIDN'T WORK.

38:56.200 --> 38:57.667
**

38:57.667 --> 38:58.700
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

38:58.700 --> 39:01.633
SO WE HAD TO, UNFORTUNATELY,

39:01.633 --> 39:04.367
MAKE THE DECISION

39:01.633 --> 39:04.367
TO PUT HIM DOWN.

39:04.367 --> 39:09.933
**

