BASICALLY, THEY SAID IT WAS

39:27.233 --> 39:31.200
A SPINAL-CORD-TYPE ISSUE --

39:31.200 --> 39:32.967
NERVES GOING TO

39:31.200 --> 39:32.967
THE BACK OF THE LEGS

39:32.967 --> 39:34.467
WERE NOT FUNCTIONING

39:32.967 --> 39:34.467
PROPERLY.

39:34.467 --> 39:36.600
HE COULD NOT FEEL

39:34.467 --> 39:36.600
HIS BACK LEGS.

39:36.600 --> 39:38.333
HE COULD NOT WALK.

39:38.333 --> 39:42.200
**

39:42.200 --> 39:44.067
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

39:44.067 --> 39:46.433
THIS IS SOMETHING

39:44.067 --> 39:46.433
THAT WOULD OCCUR IN DOGS

39:46.433 --> 39:51.333
OVER MONTHS, YEARS,

39:51.333 --> 39:55.167
SO THE FACT THAT

39:51.333 --> 39:55.167
THIS HAPPENED OUT OF NOWHERE,

39:55.167 --> 39:58.400
I MEAN,

39:55.167 --> 39:58.400
JUST IN A SPLIT SECOND --

39:58.400 --> 40:00.100
THEY COULDN'T EXPLAIN THAT.

40:00.100 --> 40:02.233
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

40:02.233 --> 40:06.500
**

40:06.500 --> 40:11.400
[ Crying ]

40:06.500 --> 40:11.400
WHEN I WALK PAST JAKE'S ASHES,

40:11.400 --> 40:14.000
I CAN'T HELP BUT THINK...

40:14.000 --> 40:16.900
**

40:16.900 --> 40:19.267
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

40:19.267 --> 40:22.667
...THAT IT WAS MY FAULT,

40:22.667 --> 40:25.333
THAT WHAT I DID

40:22.667 --> 40:25.333
BY GOING TO MANSFIELD

40:25.333 --> 40:28.267
LED TO HIS DEATH...

40:28.267 --> 40:30.567
THAT I DID THAT TO HIM.

40:30.567 --> 40:34.733
**

40:34.733 --> 40:36.733
