40:36.733 --> 40:42.033
**

40:42.033 --> 40:46.600
WHEN MY DOG DIED

40:42.033 --> 40:46.600
THREE MONTHS TO THE DAY

40:46.600 --> 40:49.000
OF ME HAVING THAT NIGHTMARE,

40:49.000 --> 40:50.733
IT KIND OF ALL CAME TOGETHER.

40:50.733 --> 40:55.933
**

40:55.933 --> 41:02.967
