40:55.933 --> 41:02.967
WHEN THE NIGHTMARES STARTED,

41:02.967 --> 41:05.333
IT WAS MAY 22nd

41:02.967 --> 41:05.333
WHEN THEY STARTED.

41:05.333 --> 41:09.500
[ SCREAMING ]

41:09.500 --> 41:12.733
I HAD THE DREAM

41:09.500 --> 41:12.733
WITH THE HELLHOUND AND MY DOG

41:12.733 --> 41:14.267
ON JULY 22nd...

41:14.267 --> 41:17.400
[ SCREAMING ]

41:17.400 --> 41:22.867
...AND ON OCTOBER 22nd,

41:17.400 --> 41:22.867
WE HAD TO PUT OUR DOG DOWN.

41:22.867 --> 41:26.700
MY HUSBAND IS NOT A BIG BELIEVER

41:22.867 --> 41:26.700
IN THE PARANORMAL,

41:26.700 --> 41:28.133
BUT THIS CHANGED.

41:28.133 --> 41:33.533
**

41:33.533 --> 41:41.100
**

41:41.100 --> 41:44.367
HE AGREES THAT

41:41.100 --> 41:44.367
HOW THIS PLAYED OUT

41:44.367 --> 41:45.900
IS JUST A LITTLE BIT TOO WEIRD

41:45.900 --> 41:49.067
TO NOT THINK THAT THERE'S

41:45.900 --> 41:49.067
SOMETHING PARANORMAL ABOUT IT

41:49.067 --> 41:52.333
WHEN YOU FACTOR IN EVERYTHING

41:49.067 --> 41:52.333
THAT HAPPENED

41:52.333 --> 41:56.800
FROM THE NIGHT I LEFT MANSFIELD

41:52.333 --> 41:56.800
UNTIL THE DAY MY DOG DIED.

41:56.800 --> 42:00.933
**

42:00.933 --> 42:04.433
IT ABSOLUTELY

42:00.933 --> 42:04.433
HAS CHANGED MY LIFE.

42:04.433 --> 42:08.700
I AM DEFINITELY

42:04.433 --> 42:08.700
A LITTLE BIT MORE CAUTIOUS

42:08.700 --> 42:11.867
WHEN IT COMES TO THE PARANORMAL.

42:11.867 --> 42:13.633
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

42:13.633 --> 42:16.267
YOU KNOW, I WOULD LIKE

42:13.633 --> 42:16.267
TO TRY TO FIND ANSWERS

42:16.267 --> 42:18.433
FOR WHAT HAPPENED TO ME.

42:18.433 --> 42:21.533
I WOULD LIKE TO FIND OUT

42:18.433 --> 42:21.533
IF ANYBODY ELSE HAS HAD

42:21.533 --> 42:25.633
THE EXACT SAME EXPERIENCE

42:21.533 --> 42:25.633
AS ME.

42:25.633 --> 42:28.800
I ALMOST WANT TO GO...

42:28.800 --> 42:33.900
AND CONFRONT

42:28.800 --> 42:33.900
AND FACE MY FEARS

42:33.900 --> 42:36.267
AND TRY TO GET

42:33.900 --> 42:36.267
SOME RESOLUTION.

42:36.267 --> 42:41.533
**

